 * functions for error handling, taking screenshots and others.
 *
 * Copyright: Timur Gafarov 2017-2026.
 * License: $(LINK2 https://boost.org/LICENSE_1_0.txt, Boost License 1.0).
 * Authors: Timur Gafarov
 */
